ğŸŒ³ Story: Aap Fruit Farm me ho
Aapke saamne ek line me trees lage hain.
Har tree ek type ka fruit deta hai (1 = apple ğŸ, 2 = banana ğŸŒ, 3 = mango ğŸ¥­) 
Aapke paas sirf 2 basket hain.
ğŸ‘‰ Rule:
Basket1 me ek type ka fruit aa sakta hai.
Basket2 me doosre type ka fruit aa sakta hai.
Dono basket unlimited hain, par 3rd type allowed nahi

ğŸ”¹ Example Fruits: [1,2,3,2,2]
(1 = apple, 2 = banana, 3 = mango)
Step 1:
Pehla tree â†’ ğŸ (apple) â†’ Basket1 me daal diya.
Basket = {ğŸ}

Step 2:
Doosra tree â†’ ğŸŒ (banana) â†’ Basket2 me daal diya.
Basket = {ğŸ, ğŸŒ}

Step 3:
Teesra tree â†’ ğŸ¥­ (mango) â†’ Arre ab problem!
Basket already 2 type se full hai (apple+banana).
Mango aa gaya â†’ basket me jagah nahi.
Rule ke hisaab se â†’ aapko pichle fruits chhodne padenge.
To hum left side se apple ko nikal dete hain.
Ab Basket = {ğŸŒ, ğŸ¥­}

Step 4:
Chautha tree â†’ ğŸŒ (banana) â†’ Already basket me hai â†’ daal do.
Basket = {ğŸŒ, ğŸ¥­}

Step 5:
Paachva tree â†’ ğŸŒ (banana) â†’ Already basket me hai â†’ daal do.
Basket = {ğŸŒ, ğŸ¥­}

ğŸ”¹ Ab Count Karein:
Continuous line me jo sabse zyada fruits collect hue â†’ [2,3,2,2]
Matlab = 4 fruits âœ…

ğŸ”¹ Samjho in Simple Words:
Aap ek window bana rahe ho â†’ ek straight line of trees.
Window me max 2 alag fruits allowed.
Jaise hi 3rd fruit aata hai â†’ window ko chhota karo (pehle wale tree chhodo).
Fir dekhte raho maximum lambi window kitni ban sakti hai.


class Solution {
public:
    int totalFruit(vector<int>& fruits) {
        
       unordered_map<int, int> basket; // fruit type -> count
        int slow = 0, maxFruits = 0;

        for (int fast = 0; fast < fruits.size(); fast++) {
            basket[fruits[fast]]++; // fast pointer se fruit uthao aur basket me daalo

            // agar basket me 2 se zyada fruit type aa gaye -> slow ko aage badhao
            while (basket.size() > 2) {
                basket[fruits[slow]]--;   // slow wala fruit hatao
                if (basket[fruits[slow]] == 0) {
                    basket.erase(fruits[slow]); // agar count 0 -> basket se nikal do
                }
                slow++; // window shrink karo
            }

            // har step pe max length calculate karo
            maxFruits = max(maxFruits, fast - slow + 1);
        }

        return maxFruits;
    }
};
